<item>
            <title>[HADOOP-7282] getRemoteIp could return null in cases where the call is ongoing but the ip went away.</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HADOOP-7282</link>
                <project id="12310240" key="HADOOP">Hadoop Common</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;getRemoteIp gets the ip from socket instead of the stored ip in Connection object. Thus calls to this function could return null when a client disconnected, but the rpc call is still ongoing...&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
